====Usage notes====
* The greeting {{m|en|hello}} is among the most universal and neutral in use. It may be heard in nearly all social situations and nearly all walks of life and is unlikely to offend.

*In the derived  senses, the word-final stress may be emphasized to focus attention, but word-initial stress is also heard in certain contexts, such as some uses of {{m|en|hello there}}, and even in isolation.

